spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: "Application\\Orchestrator"
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Orchestrator"
updatedAt: 2026-04-19
description: Top-level orchestrators — AgentRunner is the public API facade; RunOrchestrator is the central CQRS processor handling all bus messages.
files[2]{file,type,summary}:
  RunOrchestrator.php,readonly final class,"The RunOrchestrator manages the lifecycle and state transitions of an AI agent run by processing commands and handling asynchronous results from LLM steps and tool executions. It coordinates with various stores and dispatchers to maintain consistency, apply pending commands, and persist state changes through event sourcing."
  AgentRunner.php,final class,"AgentRunner orchestrates the lifecycle of agent execution runs by managing state transitions and command dispatching. It acts as a facade that coordinates between input validation, message serialization, and the underlying command bus to ensure consistent run progression."